author: Alyssa Fowers
title: How Our Top Google Searches Have Changed During The Coronavirus
description: April 2019 was a simpler time. Americans wanted to know what a black hole was, who was playing in the Final Four and how many episodes of "Game of Thrones" there were.
content:
April 2019 was a simpler time. Americans wanted to know what a black hole was, who was playing in the Final Four and how many episodes of Game of Thrones there were.
